description:
Ana de Armas is a Golden Globe– and Oscar Award–nominated actress you know from films like Knives Out, Blonde, No Time to Die, and many more. Her latest project is a starring role in the fifth film of the John Wick franchise. It's called From the World of John Wick: Ballerina set to release in theaters June 6th. But how is she with spicy food? Find out as Ana takes on the wings of death and discusses the ultimate Cuban feast, the state of the action flick, and how she would take down a bad guy with Da Bomb.
